document.full_text: e'twaun moore scored 19 points and jujuan johnson added 16 with 16 rebounds friday night as third-seeded purdue routed st. peter's 65-43.
document.title: southwest: purdue 65, st. peters 43: moore, johnson lead purdue past st. peter's
